settings_modCat1_setting10_name: "Frequency of equipment checks (1-100)"
settings_modCat1_setting10_desc: "(Performance setting) Lower values will check equipped items more often.
 This gives faster visible updates of ring changes,
 but possibly cause stutters from increased garbage collection."
